{
  "id": "s1_cena_famiglia",
  "audio_theme": "ritorno_casa",
  "stat_entry": [
    {
      "stat": "legame",
      "op": "gte",
      "value": 70,
      "goto_branch": "intro_calda",
      "prepend": true
    }
  ],
  "pages": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p0_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Evening. The kitchen smells of butter and eggs. Mallow is at the stove with the air of someone about to reveal a family secret."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Two eggs. Crack them like this, put the cheese inside, fold them like a calzone. Fry in butter. My grandma called it calzuovo — egg-calzone."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex stares at him from the high chair. Not at the calzuovo. At him. With detective eyes."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "Calzuovo. I like it. Sounds like something you eat and then go into battle."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p0_a_t5",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Exactly. It's the warrior's dish. Or at least the hungry programmer's."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p1_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "The calzuovo arrives at the table. Mallow serves it with the pride of a Michelin-starred chef. Lex looks at it. Then at Favilla. Then back at Mallow."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t2",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "He's plotting. I can see it. Same face as the pasta aisle."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex pushes his plate away. He doesn't eat. He squints. Points his little finger toward Favilla, then toward Mallow. Like a silent conductor."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t4",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "What's up with you tonight? Don't you like calzuovo?"
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p1_a_t5",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "It's not the calzuovo. It's his mother. He's trying to tell you."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p2_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla",
            "lex"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Lex has now staged a small sabotage. The spoon falls. Then the cup. Then three more things in rapid succession. Each time he points at Favilla."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t2",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Mallow looks at him. Then at Favilla. Then back at Lex. Something clicks."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t3",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "You know what's weird? For the past few weeks, every time something... strange happens, Lex looks at you. Not me. You."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p2_a_t4",
              "type": "thought",
              "speaker": "favilla",
              "text": "He knows. He doesn't know. But he feels it. And Lex is serving it to him on a silver platter."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
      "panels": [
        {
          "id": "cena_p3_a",
          "characters": [
            "mallow",
            "favilla"
          ],
          "text_blocks": [
            {
              "id": "cena_p3_a_t1",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "Mallow puts down his fork. Dinner is half-eaten. Lex has stopped throwing things and now stares at his father with almost comical intensity."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p3_a_t2",
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speaker": "mallow",
              "text": "Favilla. There's something you're not telling me."
            },
            {
              "id": "cena_p3_a_t3",
              "type": "narration",
              "text": "He's not angry. He's... tender. Like he's asking permission to know. Lex holds his breath."
            }
          ],
          "choice": {
            "id": "cena_choice",
            "prompt": "Mallow is looking at you. Lex too. Dinner is a powder keg.",
            "options": [
              {
                "id": "confessa_piccolo",
                "label": "«Mallow... I need to tell you something. That Sunday at the park...»",
                "goto_branch": "branch_confessa",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "legame": 8,
                  "segreto": -10
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "confessa_piccolo"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "facciata",
                "label": "«Lex, eat. Mallow, this is delicious. Everything's fine.»",
                "goto_branch": "branch_facciata",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "segreto": 8,
                  "resistenza": 5
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "facciata"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "umorismo",
                "label": "«Mallow, your son is trying to be a matchmaker. Or maybe a film director.»",
                "goto_branch": "branch_umorismo",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "legame": 5,
                  "scintille": 5
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "umorismo"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "distrai_lex",
                "label": "You glance at Lex. He has crayons. He's drawing something.",
                "stat_effects": {
                  "segreto": -3
                },
                "set_flags": {
                  "cena_famiglia_fatta": true
                },
                "set_memories": {
                  "choice.s1_cena_famiglia": "distrai_lex"
                },
                "minigame": {
                  "type": "disegna",
                  "tiers": [
                    {
                      "min": 4,
                      "label": "Innocent drawing.",
                      "goto_branch": "branch_disegno_innocuo",
                      "stat_effects": {
                        "legame": 8,
                        "scintille": 5
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "min": 2,
                      "label": "Almost...",
                      "goto_branch": "branch_disegno_quasi",
                      "stat_effects": {
                        "segreto": -5,
                        "legame": 3
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "min": 0,
                      "label": "Mallow saw.",
                      "goto_branch": "branch_disegno_visto",
                      "stat_effects": {
                        "segreto": -12,
                        "legame": 5
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "branches": {
    "intro_calda": {
      "id": "intro_calda",
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "intro_calda_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow spent the afternoon cooking. The calzuovo isn't just a recipe — it's his way of saying 'I love you' without having to say it."
                },
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla knows this. And it's exactly this warmth she risks losing if he ever finds out everything."
                },
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "I figured after the week you've had... you deserved a real dinner."
                },
                {
                  "id": "intro_calda_a_t4",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex watches from the high chair. Calculating. Tonight, dad is on his side."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_confessa": {
      "id": "branch_confessa",
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_confessa_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla puts down her fork. Lex stops breathing — or at least seems to, for a seven-and-a-half-month-old."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "That Sunday at the park... something happened. I don't know how to explain it. Not even to myself."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow says nothing. He takes her hand. He waits."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "When you're ready, I'm here. I'm not going anywhere."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_a_t5",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Not the whole truth. But a piece of it. Enough for tonight."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_confessa_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex releases his breath. Then smiles — that accomplice smile with two tiny teeth that only Favilla can decipher."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "The calzuovo is almost cold. But Mallow's hand is still there, on top of hers."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_confessa_b_t3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Let's eat, before it gets cold. Then you can tell me the rest."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_facciata": {
      "id": "branch_facciata",
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_facciata_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla smiles. It's a well-practiced smile. She changes the subject with the fluidity of someone who's been doing it for months."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Everything's fine, really. Just tired. La Corvi, the inspection. Heavy week. But this calzuovo is a miracle."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow nods. But he hasn't stopped looking at her. Lex huffs — frustrated, theatrical, definitive."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_a_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "I lied to him again. And Lex knows. And he's mad at me."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_facciata_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow goes back to eating. He talks about work, a new JavaScript library. The evening derails into normality."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "But Lex won't look at her anymore. His arms are crossed on the high chair. Seven months old and already capable of holding a grudge."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_facciata_b_t3",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "I kept the secret. But I lost something with my son. I'll get it back tomorrow. Or maybe not."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_umorismo": {
      "id": "branch_umorismo",
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_umorismo_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla looks at Lex. Then at Mallow. Then bursts out laughing — that real, full laugh that hasn't come out in days."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Mallow, look at him. He has the face of someone trying to make us divorce. Is he our baby, or a tiny secret agent?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex makes a face — a kind of raspberry that sounds like 'I'm not a secret agent but I'm working on it'."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "He's got more charisma than me. I say that with pride and a little fear."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "branch_umorismo_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "All three of them laugh at the same moment. The calzuovo is gone, but it doesn't matter. For an instant, it's just a family having dinner."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex falls asleep shortly after, his head drooping. But he's smiling. He won something, even if he doesn't know what yet."
                },
                {
                  "id": "branch_umorismo_b_t3",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Tomorrow everything will be complicated again. But tonight it's not. Tonight is ours."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_disegno_innocuo": {
      "id": "branch_disegno_innocuo",
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_innocuo_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex stares at his own drawing. The mom with fire hair now has normal hair. The sparkles have become... stars? The pointing finger is now a waving hand."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "His masterpiece has been altered. By someone with a gray crayon and suspicious knowledge of his plan."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex glares at Favilla with the expression of someone who just lost a game of chess. Mallow walks over, looks at the paper."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "What a beautiful drawing! Is that us? Look, that's you, those are me and mom."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_innocuo_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t1",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Yes. The three of us."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow smiles. Lex crosses his arms in the high chair. Defeated. For now."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "The calzuovo is almost gone. The drawing is innocent. And Lex has learned that mom is faster than him even at the dinner table."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_innocuo_b_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Nice try, little one. But tonight I win."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_disegno_quasi": {
      "id": "branch_disegno_quasi",
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_2.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_quasi_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla quickly modifies what she can. The result is a strange drawing: a figure with hair half yellow and half gray, another figure that seems to be looking but also not."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "A crayon rolls away. Lex follows it with his eyes. Favilla picks it up before Mallow notices."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "What's that? Let me see."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "A self-portrait by Lex. Abstract. He's talented."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_1.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_quasi_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex glares at her. Mallow laughs:"
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "He's talented."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "But he hesitated a second too long before laughing. That second where he looked at the drawing more carefully than necessary."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_quasi_b_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "He didn't get it. But he felt there's something to get. Tomorrow he'll think about it again."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "branch_disegno_visto": {
      "id": "branch_disegno_visto",
      "pages": [
        {
          "index": 0,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_visto_a",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "lex",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow approaches while Favilla still has the crayon in her hand. Too late. He sees the original drawing: the figure with fire hair, the other watching, Lex pointing."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Who's that?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "He points at the fire hair. Favilla grabs the paper, crumples it."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_a_t4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Nothing. Kids' stuff."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "background": "assets/episodes/prologo/page_3.png",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "disegno_visto_b",
              "characters": [
                "favilla",
                "mallow",
                "lex"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "But Mallow doesn't look away. Lex smiles — he won."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "They look like... glowing hair. Like the one in the video."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "The silence lasts a second. Lex looks at Mallow. Mallow looks at Favilla. Favilla looks at the crumpled paper."
                },
                {
                  "id": "disegno_visto_b_t4",
                  "type": "thought",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "He connected the drawing to the video. My son just outplayed me. With a crayon."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "epilogue": {
    "id": "epilogue",
    "pages": [
      {
        "index": 0,
